        "content": "<p>Could you first define the S, as a function with a domain and codomain. As in just where it lives. For your lemma you can use the hypothesis that that PV = NRT, etc in your lemma , as well as appropriate differentiability assumptions. </p>\n<p>It would help a lot to have for reference a very rigorous pen and paper proof.</p>\n<p>The first step is to state the theorems statement , and then use sorry as a placeholder, checking the definitions are doing what you expect  </p>\n<p>I think what you are trying to say is possible to formalise, but mathlib works in full generality so it would be a lot of abstract machinery applied to very specific cases.</p>",
